## 4. Liability & Warranty Disclaimer / Sorumluluk ve Garanti Reddi

- The mod is provided "AS IS" with no warranties. The author is not liable for any damages, data loss, server issues, performance problems, or other losses arising from use of the mod.
- Users install and run the mod at their own risk.
- This disclaimer is consistent with the MIT license terms included in `LICENSE`.

