## 5. Malicious or Illegal Use / Kötüye Kullanım

- Any illegal, malicious, or rule-violating use of this mod (cheating, harming servers/players, distributing malware, etc.) is the sole responsibility of the user performing that action.
- The author expressly disclaims responsibility for misuse. If misuse or harm is reported, the author may request removal of the mod from the offending distribution or contact relevant platform maintainers.

---

## 6. Enforcement & Takedown / İhlal ve Kaldırma Süreci

If license terms or attribution requirements are violated:

1. The author will attempt to notify the distributor/pack maintainer and request correction.
2. If unresolved, the author may file takedown or DMCA/licensing reports with the hosting platform (GitHub, Modrinth, CurseForge, YouTube, etc.) or pursue other legal remedies.

Please contact the author first to resolve issues amicably.

---

