## 9. File naming & capitalization / Dosya isimleri ve büyük harf kullanımı

- Place this file at the repository root as `TERMS_OF_USE.md` (uppercase with underscores) — GitHub and users commonly recognize this.
- Keep the license file named `LICENSE` (all caps) in the repo root.
- Internal headings may use Title Case for readability; capitalization in headings does not change legal meaning.

