## 10. Legal note / Hukuki not

I am not a lawyer. This document is practical guidance to make attribution, liability, and enforcement expectations clear. For binding legal advice or a custom enforceable agreement (for example, to require mandatory social‑media tagging as a legal condition), consult a qualified attorney.
